<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>The Studio // Sandbox Utilities</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-panel text-ink antialiased">
    
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-16 pt-16 sm:pt-24">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-coral">
        Experimental Sandbox
      </p>

      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:justify-between gap-2 border-b border-line pb-6">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl text-ink">
          The Studio Workspace
        </h1>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-ink-soft">
          By <span class="text-ink font-medium">Bljeona</span> — Independent Tools
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-4">
          <p class="font-display text-xl sm:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-ink font-medium">
            A playful deck of independent workflow toys and custom client utilities.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-ink-soft max-w-2xl">
            These tools securely manage calculations and design transformations entirely on the client side. Zero backends, zero server overhead, built purely for personal speed, convenience, and daily developer utility.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5 bg-panel border border-line p-5 rounded-sm grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <h4 class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-soft">
              Architecture
            </h4>
            <p class="font-body text-xs text-ink leading-snug">
              Astro Components, Pure Tailwind, Local Storage
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1 border-l border-line pl-4">
            <h4 class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-soft">
              Runtime Status
            </h4>
            <p class="font-body text-xs text-coral font-semibold tracking-wide leading-snug">
              $0.00 Server Footprint
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        
        <div class="group flex flex-col justify-between border border-line p-6 rounded-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-coral/40 bg-white">
          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <div>
                <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest bg-coral/10 text-coral px-2 py-0.5 rounded-sm font-semibold">
                  Utility App
                </span>
                <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-ink tracking-tight transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:text-coral">
                  Timetracker
                </h2>
              </div>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-ink-soft/40 font-semibold select-none">01 / 02</span>
            </div>

            <p class="font-body text-sm text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">
              A mobile-first workflow time portal built to replace spreadsheet logs. Automatically checks hour balances and handles tracking variables directly via local client memory arrays.
            </p>

            <div class="relative aspect-[16/10] bg-panel border border-line rounded-sm overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-ink/[0.01] transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-0"></div>
              
              <img 
                src="/timetracker-preview.jpg" 
                alt="Timetracker App Frame Layout Interface Overview" 
                class="w-[70%] max-h-[85%] object-contain shadow-md rounded-sm border border-line transform rotate-1 group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-[1.03] transition-all duration-300"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-line flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-xs">
            <a href="/studio/timetracker" class="text-ink font-medium group-hover:text-coral transition-colors flex items-center gap-1.5">
              Launch Interface &rarr;
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group flex flex-col justify-between border border-line p-6 rounded-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-coral/40 bg-white">
          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <div>
                <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest bg-coral/10 text-coral px-2 py-0.5 rounded-sm font-semibold">
                  Design Engine
                </span>
                <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-ink tracking-tight transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:text-coral">
                  Colors Hub
                </h2>
              </div>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-ink-soft/40 font-semibold select-none">02 / 02</span>
            </div>

            <p class="font-body text-sm text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">
              A color generator workspace designed to build production pallets. Dynamically inspects token outputs, tests functional WCAG contrast scores, and controls custom OKLCH spectrum shifts.
            </p>

            <div class="relative aspect-[16/10] bg-panel border border-line rounded-sm flex flex-col justify-between p-4 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1 opacity-30">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-ink"></span>
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-ink"></span>
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-ink"></span>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-2.5 transform -rotate-1 group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-[1.01] transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-1.5">
                  <div class="h-8 rounded-sm bg-coral/10 border border-coral/20 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-[9px] text-coral font-semibold">100</div>
                  <div class="h-8 rounded-sm bg-coral/30 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-[9px] text-ink">200</div>
                  <div class="h-8 rounded-sm bg-coral/60 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-[9px] text-ink">300</div>
                  <div class="h-8 rounded-sm bg-coral/80 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-[9px] text-white">400</div>
                  <div class="h-8 rounded-sm bg-coral flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-[9px] text-white font-semibold">500</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="p-2 bg-white/40 border border-line text-[9px] font-mono text-ink-soft flex justify-between items-center rounded-sm">
                  <span class="truncate">--brand-coral: oklch(65% 0.24 28);</span>
                  <span class="text-coral font-bold px-1 select-none">AAA</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="font-mono text-[8px] text-ink-soft/30 text-right uppercase tracking-wider select-none">
                Spectrum Matrix
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-line flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-xs">
            <a href="/studio/colorshub" class="text-ink font-medium group-hover:text-coral transition-colors flex items-center gap-1.5">
              Open Workspace &rarr;
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </main>
    
  </body>
</html>